[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m thinking about how if the child TraceFactory calls Class.forName on a custom nested within the parent, it could lead to a ClassCastException because the class isn’t assignable to the child TraceFactory. So, the custom factory needs to be either generated as bytecode for the child loader or exist as a test class that references the child TraceFactory. Since the classpath includes test classes, the child-first classloader could load a duplicate copy of the nested CustomTraceFactory and TraceFactoryTest. I need the custom class to be public!
[thinking] 
